# AibriefAI Launch Infrastructure — Zero-Cost Stack

## Confirmed launch stack

```text
Hosting: Render Static Site free tier
Public URL: https://aibriefai.onrender.com
Primary LLM: Google Gemini API free tier
Fallback LLM: Groq Llama 3.3 70B free tier
Pipeline: GitHub Actions every 5 minutes
Monitoring: UptimeRobot + Sentry free tiers
Monthly cost target: $0.00
```

## Render

`render.yaml` defines a static site:

```yaml
services:
  - type: web
    name: aibriefai
    runtime: static
    plan: free
    buildCommand: "true"
    staticPublishPath: ./web
    autoDeployTrigger: commit
    renderSubdomainPolicy: enabled
```

Render only serves static files. GitHub Actions runs the pipeline and commits generated dashboard artifacts.

## GitHub secrets

```bash
gh secret set GEMINI_API_KEY
gh secret set GROQ_API_KEY
gh secret set SENTRY_DSN
gh secret set GITHUB_TOKEN

gh variable set GEMINI_MODEL --body gemini-2.5-flash
gh variable set GROQ_MODEL --body llama-3.3-70b-versatile
```

## Health and monitoring

```text
Health URL: https://aibriefai.onrender.com/health
UptimeRobot interval: 5 minutes
Alert email: Fmg_511@hotmail.com
```

GitHub Actions staleness workflow fails if `web/data/signals.json` has not received a commit in more than 15 minutes.

